==English==

===Etymology===
Latin ''[[extendere]]'' ‘stretch out’.

===Verb===
'''extend'''  ([[extends]], [[extended]], [[extending]])

# Make larger in [[area]] or [[extent]].
# Cause to last longer.
# extend (1) one’s limbs or muscles

